!-   ===========  ALL OBJECTS IN CLASS: OUTPUT:JSON ===========

Output:JSON,
    TimeSeriesAndTabular,    !- Option Type
    No,                      !- Output JSON
    No,                      !- Output CBOR
    No;                      !- Output MessagePack


